import { Button, Card, Col, Container, Form, Row } from "react-bootstrap";
import React from "react";

function ProfileDetails() {
  return (
    <Form className="mx-auto w-75">
      <Form.Group as={Row} controlId="formProfileDetailsName">
        <Form.Label column className="sr-only">
          FirstName
        </Form.Label>
        <Col sm="7">
          <Form.Control plaintext type="text" placeholder="First Name" />
        </Col>
        <Form.Label column className="sr-only">
          LastName
        </Form.Label>
        <Col sm="7">
          <Form.Control plaintext type="text" placeholder="Last Name" />
        </Col>
      </Form.Group>
      <Form.Group as={Row} controlId="formProfileDetailsTitle">
        <Form.Label column className="sr-only">
          Title
        </Form.Label>
        <Col sm="14">
          <Form.Control plaintext type="text" placeholder="Title" />
        </Col>
      </Form.Group>
      <Form.Group as={Row} controlId="formProfileDetailsLocation">
        <Form.Label column className="sr-only">
          Location
        </Form.Label>
        <Col sm="14">
          <Form.Control
            plaintext
            type="text"
            placeholder="Location"
          />
        </Col>
      </Form.Group>
      <Button hidden type="submit">
        Save
      </Button>
    </Form>
  );
}

export default ProfileDetails;
